title: [Icemule Trace, East Road]
description: Short, sturdy buildings line both sides of the road here, providing homes to the merchants of Icemule Trace.  A gnarled and twisted tree guards the south edge of the road, its roots snaking along the dirt road underfoot.  Beneath the tree, a scattering of leaves litter the ground.

Short, sturdy buildings line both sides of the road here, providing homes to the merchants of Icemule Trace.  A gnarled and twisted tree guards the south edge of the road, its roots snaking along the dirt road underfoot.  Beneath the tree, a scattering of leaves litter the ground about a a snow-covered cottage with a simple parchment sign tacked to the door.
